      "abstract": "1. Introduction 2. Why QCD? 3. Basics of QCD 4. Infra-red safety and non-safety 5. Libby-Sterman analysis and power counting 6. Parton model to parton theory I 7. Parton model to parton theory II 8. Factorization 9. Corrections to the parton model in QCD 10. Factorization and subtractions 11. DIS in QCD 12. Fragmentation 13. TMD factorization 14. Hadron-hadron collisions 15. More advanced topics Appendices References Index."
